# Design system

Before editing styles:

1. Read [src/styles/DESIGN_SYSTEM.md](src/styles/DESIGN_SYSTEM.md) for rules and semantics
2. Read [src/styles/variables.css](src/styles/variables.css) for token values
3. Use `var(--*)` only — no raw hex/hsl for colors, no ad-hoc rem for spacing
4. `@keyframes` belong in `animations.css` only
5. Run `pnpm lint:style` on changed files
